         MACRO                                                                  
.*  added by choyt 05/05/92                                                     
.*  purge anything in the terminal seg buffer.                                  
.*  do not write it out.  just get rid of it for all time.                      
.*                                                                              
&L       TPURGE &OPTIONS                                                        
&L       LABEL                                                                  
         CLEAR CPSEGLENF                                                        
         CLEAR CPSEGMRKF                                                        
         MEND                                                                   
